## Error Codes Reference

### Facebook
- `content_unavailable` - Page content not available
- `redirected_away` - Redirected off Facebook domain
- `login_required` - Login page shown (inconclusive)
- `insufficient_content` - Response too short
- `content_read_timeout` - Timeout reading response

### Instagram
- `redirect_to_login` - Redirected to login/explore
- `error_page_detected` - Error page content found
- `cloudflare_challenge` - Blocked by Cloudflare
- `unclear_response` - Could not determine validity
- `timeout` - Page load timeout
- `browser_error` - Playwright error

### Twitter
- `account_not_found` - Account doesn't exist/suspended
- `cloudflare_challenge` - Blocked by Cloudflare
- `unclear_response` - Could not determine validity
- `timeout` - Page load timeout
- `browser_error` - Playwright error

### LinkedIn
- HTTP status code as string (`404`, `429`, `999`, etc.)

### General
- `timeout` / `server_timeout` - Request timeout
- Various aiohttp exception names

