## Best Practices

### When Adding New Social Media Platforms

1. Add domain detection in `detect_social_media_platform()`
2. Create `check_<platform>()` function
3. Add case in `check_platform()` dispatcher
4. Define error indicators specific to the platform
5. Test with both valid and invalid profiles

### When Modifying Detection Logic

1. Be conservative - prefer `error` status over false `broken`
2. Use specific error indicators (not generic text that might appear on valid pages)
3. Check for login/challenge pages that make results inconclusive
4. Log detection decisions for debugging

